videos.description: Michael Young intercepts the pass and finds  Damon Wilson who hits the tough layup for Pittsburgh.
videos.headline: Pittsburgh's steal leads to Wilson's tough layup

videos.description: Joel Berry misses the 3 point but Luke Maye gets the offensive rebound and puts it back at the buzzer for North Carolina.
videos.headline: UNC gets the offensive rebound and put back just as half expires

videos.description: Kennedy Meeks gets the steal and Nate Britt threads the needle to Isaiah Hicks for the UNC dunk.
videos.headline: UNC gets the steal and uses a great pass for the dunk

videos.description: Sean  Farnham and Karl Ravech break down North Carolina's win and the Tarheels upcoming  schedule.
videos.headline: Breaking down North Carolina's 80-78 victory over Pittsburgh
